desc: Frozen Meals to your Door New Zealand wide

layout.text: Lovingly crafted Chef made meals in your freezer

Delicious, generous portions of nutrient packed meals - with no added nasties!
These chef made meals are produced in Jay's restaurant Kitchen with super-fresh local produce and ingredients.
Our hearty portions are vac packed to lock in the freshness & flavour and snap frozen at the peak of freshness to capture the nutrients and goodness that kiwi's deserve!
Delivered overnight & ready to eat in minutes!
